-# What's new in 1.1:
-
-1. Static api doesn't take context anymore. Hence
-
-        Book.findById(context, Book.class, 1);
-
-        becomes
-
-        Book.findById(Book.class, 1);
-
-
-2. Some cleanup in the code.
